test_negate_of_lists:
assert [91] == [-91]
  At index 0 diff: 91 != -91
  Full diff:
  - [-91]
  ?  -
  + [91]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [91] == [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 91 != 0
  Right contains 7 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
  + [91]
test_non_divisibles_1:
assert [91] == []
  Left contains one more item: 91
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [91]
